{"name":"James Raynor","nameCn":"詹姆斯·雷诺","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/dd/3c/19225_crt_19PTI.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>詹姆斯·雷诺</li><li><span>别名: </span>吉姆·雷诺</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Jim</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>吉姆</li><li><span>性别: </span>男</li><li><span>恋人: </span>莎拉·路易丝·凯瑞甘</li>","detail":"吉姆·雷诺是暴雪娱乐出品的《星际争霸》系列游戏中的一个主要虚构角色，主要由克里斯·梅森和詹姆斯·菲尼所创。其外貌形态则由克里斯·梅森设计。<br />雷诺在游戏中起初是在玛尔·莎拉殖民行星的一位29岁的人族民兵队长。随后他加入了阿克图尔斯·蒙斯克的反叛组织柯哈之子对抗人族联邦，但逐渐对其失去了信心，而因此组建了他个人的军队。他深爱身为人类时的莎拉·路易丝·凯瑞甘，以至会被刀锋女皇利用。其更加丰富的人物形象包含在了小说《利伯蒂的远征》和《刀锋女皇》中。在游戏中，雷诺通常驾驶着一架秃鹰雷车出现，有时也会出现为一个机枪兵单位，或者海伯利昂号战列巡洋舰的舰长。作为《星际争霸》系列的主要角色之一，吉姆·雷诺的角色深度和配音品质得到了媒体的好评。在GameSpot的一项调查中，雷诺当选了十大电子游戏英雄之一。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/1647","name":"StarCraft II: Wings of Liberty","nameCn":"星际争霸2：自由之翼","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/8d/42/1647_xkK2x.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"Robert Clotworthy","castHref":"/person/39744","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/b9/bd/39744_prsn_9vaFv.jpg","type":4},{"href":"/subject/608","name":"StarCraft","nameCn":"星际争霸","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/99/6a/608_WWws6.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"Robert Clotworthy","castHref":"/person/39744","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/b9/bd/39744_prsn_9vaFv.jpg","type":4},{"href":"/subject/116285","name":"Heroes of the Storm","nameCn":"风暴英雄","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/1c/66/116285_L2uyh.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"Robert Clotworthy","castHref":"/person/39744","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/b9/bd/39744_prsn_9vaFv.jpg","type":4},{"href":"/subject/118410","name":"StarCraft II: Legacy of the Void","nameCn":"星际争霸2：虚空之遗","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/f5/1a/118410_ckuAy.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"Robert Clotworthy","castHref":"/person/39744","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/b9/bd/39744_prsn_9vaFv.jpg","type":4},{"href":"/subject/88413","name":"Starcraft: brood war","nameCn":"星际争霸：母巢之战","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover